          "reviewBody": "\n\nWe are deeply grateful to this wonderful school and its dedicated teachers. Without any tuition support, our daughter was able to score 94% in the Tenth Board Exam 2026, with marks above 96 in three subjects.\n\nThis achievement is not just hers, it reflects the sincere effort, care, and guidance of every teacher. Our heartfelt thanks to the Management, Principal, Vice Principal, and each member of the staff for shaping her journey with such commitment.\n\nWith happiness and trust, she has now taken admission to Plus One at her beloved school. Our younger one is also here, moving into Third Standard.\n\nThank you from the bottom of our hearts for being such a strong part of our children’s lives.",
